Harry H. Corbett https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harry_H._Corbett 0 Harry H. Corbett, OBE (28 February 1925 – 21 March 1982) was an English actor and comedian. Corbett is best known for his co-starring role in the popular and long-running BBC Television sitcom Steptoe and Son which was first broadcast from 1962–1965 and 1970–1974.
